description:
Welcome to PART 2 the GRAND FINALE of the 2025 J vs Ben season! We have clipped together every J vs Ben for the entire year so you can relive it all and find out who the grand champion is!  From the “In the Movies,” “Quotes Quizes,” and “Open Book,” formats we had a lot of curve balls this year.

Huge thanks to all the quiz masters throughout the year! We could not make the show without you and look forward to all of your questions next year!
